data.ProductDescription: With our two transactional banking packages designed for Small Businesses, you could save on transaction fees and get the practical support you need to take that next step with your business. Starting Up and been trading less than 24 months? This 2 year package could be perfect for your business.  In year 1 no transaction fees (as detailed in the Transaction Fees on Business Accounts section of the Schedule of Charges for Business Customers) will apply to your current account. In year 2 a 50% discount on these Transaction fees will apply.
data.ProductName: BCA in Year 1 of the Small Business Startup Package (FRCs 61)
